message.raw:
Added sample_rate_DO and sample_rate_AO to the object signature:

NI_DAQmx(name='ni_pci_6733_0', parent_device=pulseblaster_0_ni_pci_clock,
         MAX_name='Dev1',
         clock_terminal='/Dev1/RTSI0',
         num_AO=8,
         sample_rate_AO=700e3, # Max sample rate
         num_DO=8,
         sample_rate_DO=1e6, # Max sample rate
         num_AI=0,
         clock_terminal_AI='/Dev1/PFI0', # Unused
         sample_rate_AI=1000,  # Interpreted as a max sample rate in triggered mode
         mode_AI='labscript', # 'labscript', 'gated', 'triggered' # Unused
         num_PFI=8 # Unused
)
